-- Prisa Climbs After Liberty Investors Approve $867 Million Investment Plan
-- B y   P a u l   T o b i n
-- 2010-11-25T08:01:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-25/prisa-climbs-after-liberty-investors-approve-867-million-investment-plan.html
Promotora de Informaciones SA gained
as much as 2.8 percent in Madrid trading after the shareholders
of Liberty Acquisition Holdings Corp. approved a plan to invest
in the Spanish media company.  Liberty investors will receive stakes collectively
amounting to more than 50 percent of Prisa in exchange for about
650 million euros in cash.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Tobin at 
 ptobin@bloomberg.net  